{"tid":456534,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【佛門多醜聞】在中國偷方丈文物坐監，轉頭到香港寶蓮寺做高層","createTime":"2017-11-03T04:47:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-03T05:48:19.000Z","uid":39464,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"73211d65633fc067b21e3005961f2a92fdbb5601","tid":456534,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T04:47:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://vmagimg.next.hk/images/apple/20171101/large/1509539514_c1e8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvmagimg.next.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple%2F20171101%2Flarge%2F1509539514_c1e8.jpg&h=d3043715&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「因為香港出家人數目不足，所以我們希望有更多出家人來參加香港的僧團。但我們發現有很多內地來的僧人在內地去了佛學院，學懂了如何唸經和做儀式。但他們並沒有一個出家的心。下班的時候，他們是會喝酒、吃肉、去夜總會。」<br />\n<br />\n翁靜晶亦曾接獲有關品格行為有問題的和尚來港的投訴。「寶蓮寺裡面有一位法師，來自福建的慕西寺。佢在內地曾趁寺院方丈去了新加坡旅行，潛入方丈室，撬開了鎖，偷了方丈室裡面所有的文物。」<br />\n<br />\n根據本刊收到的內地判決書，當時法號妙持的瞿慶如，在零四年與另外一名和尚，偷取泉州市慕西寺方丈室內的佛像、字畫及玉器等，經法院調查和審理而被判監兩年六個月。但翁靜晶指出，他出獄後竟然來了香港，並在寶蓮寺擔當維那（負責統理寺內法會進行）。翁直斥事情離譜，又認為香港的入境政策出了問題。「為什麼呢個人當時以一個和尚的身份，犯了盜竊案，佢無因為咁樣破戒而還俗，仲可以繼續做和尚，申請來港，來港後仲可以在一間這樣大的寺廟裡面做這樣的職位？」<br />\n<br />\n寶蓮寺助理回應指，寶蓮寺是開戒的道場，每三年開戒一次，會有來自世界各地的人來參與，所謂「開戒」，所指的是讓人學習做和尚並成為和尚，男助理確認該人曾參與過開戒，在港學習成為和尚，但現在沒有留在寶蓮寺，他表示：「本寺法師名單沒有這名法師。」<br />\n<br />\n撰文：黃心悅、鄭靖而，文倩儀<br />\n攝影：韋平、王晴、海江田<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://nextplus.nextmedia.com/news/latest/20171102/556936\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Flatest%2F20171102%2F556936&d=3qMKKJj68wuM9hR5Hap%2FotibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=f29b3eb2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Flatest%2F20171102%2F556936&h=775af268\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://nextplus.nextmedia.com/news/latest/20171102/556936</a>"},{"pid":"443e111550115442bed21f1debb1c1df1e655a85","tid":456534,"uid":49588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T04:50:42.000Z","msg":"輸入中國磚材！"},{"pid":"5f45e5d3871af988910b4851c2c7b0ba24527e9d","tid":456534,"uid":63909,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T04:51:07.000Z","msg":"翁靜晶係有心人<br />\n係咁追住班大陸假佛門中人<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c63e6afd6f60fb4c62833fb8634c975f46d8f96","tid":456534,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T05:03:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>翁靜晶係有心人<br />\n係咁追住班大陸假佛門中人<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8eb1dc6f73648282940e6f5a278de5e3e8c2741c","tid":456534,"uid":38671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T05:05:43.000Z","msg":"咁都可以黎香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"143717d75215a38ad7e802c68cc5f17b827615cc","tid":456534,"uid":28279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T05:15:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁都可以黎香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n輸入犯罪專才"},{"pid":"32636516967c71e4c836a1c9dd23f396768d776f","tid":456534,"uid":118120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T05:22:52.000Z","msg":"善信既燈油錢就係咁樣俾左呢班假和尚吃喝玩樂"},{"pid":"7cbc77dbd9ec0fda800bab3702d4d11fcfaa1267","tid":456534,"uid":10157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T05:25:17.000Z","msg":"廢老信佛撚又跳出話搞三搞四"},{"pid":"ab9cd6b994901f3d4c41d4072ad055ff9812f0fd","tid":456534,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T05:38:24.000Z","msg":"N年前高登仲捧佛反耶<br />\n殊不知佛撚仲狼過耶<br />\n偷呃騙范范撈齊<br />\n香港佛門簡直係一群支那犯罪集團"},{"pid":"6a8a559b98a9f75856b766dbeea0760fc9b031fd","tid":456534,"uid":34857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T05:38:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>善信既燈油錢就係咁樣俾左呢班假和尚吃喝玩樂</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我有朋友前排去寺做維修工程，<br />\nlunch time d大陸和尚食肉，玩手機<br />\n同d工友講叫雞經<br />\n<br />\n利申發夢聽到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"944149dbee62b5ecaa2256135ae28ddbffcb3d8b","tid":456534,"uid":34517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T05:48:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>N年前高登仲捧佛反耶<br />\n殊不知佛撚仲狼過耶<br />\n偷呃騙范范撈齊<br />\n香港佛門簡直係一群支那犯罪集團</blockquote><br />\n依家連登都係咁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n見到耶就屌左先<br />\n見到和尚犯法就話佛教係哲學<br />\n只係現代人扭曲左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}